// Item spawn results interface (custom dev tool). The ::~item command fills the
// dev_itemsearch inventory with search matches, and itemspawn.rs2 owns the
// buttons/count dialogs/spawning behavior.
//   left-click (option1) = Spawn  (asks for amount)
//   right-click          = Spawn noted (asks for amount) / Spawn 1 / Spawn 100 / Info

